Class Dose

java.lang.Object
app.core.domain.model.Dose
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Dose>
public class Dose extends Object implements Comparable<Dose>, Serializable
It represents a dose through dose number, dosage and a time interval between last dose.
